{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":22759,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":3801,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"有道理","timestamp":1592891146,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":22760,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":3801,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"赞同 不歧视lgbt，但对他们有偏见，因为他们还要管到别人脑子里在想什么 呕","timestamp":1592891150,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":22813,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":3801,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"偏见是态度 歧视是行动","timestamp":1592891332,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":22815,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":3801,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Bob: 没人管你脑子里怎么想，只要不表现出歧视。可是现实生活中到处都有歧视","timestamp":1592891336,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":22856,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":3801,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"？\n当你表现出偏见，不就已经是把偏见外化了吗？","timestamp":1592891475,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":22923,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":3801,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Eve: 如果对着当事人表现出偏见我觉得已经算一种歧视了，等同于日常生活中你跟喜欢吃苹果的人说吃苹果的人好恶心，就是一种不尊重、待人不公平的行为。只要做到尊重他人，论心不论迹就好。","timestamp":1592891735,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":23097,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":3801,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 帮捉虫 论迹不论心","timestamp":1592892267,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":23316,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":3801,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Carol: 啊是的！感谢🙏","timestamp":1592893056,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":5,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":3801,"reply":8,"tag":null,"text":"似乎很多人不明白偏见和歧视这两个词的区别啊。人怀有偏见很正常，莫名不喜欢某个特征的人也非常非常正常，但歧视一词，是相当于把你的偏见外化，在你所偏见的内容不对任何人造成负面影响的前提下，对你偏见的事物持有不公正对待，这叫歧视。所以歧视无论如何都不是一个我们应该有的处世方法，也希望各位在讨论的时候说明白自己只是不喜欢吃榴莲，还是看到吃榴莲的种榴莲的就会向他吐痰。","timestamp":1592891034,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782585,"url":"","vote":{}}}